    "Different shared tasks, where research groups tackle the same problem or dataset with a defined outcome metric, have been announced with the aim of automatically fact-checking claims.",
    "For example, the shared task RUMOUREVAL provided a dataset of \"dubious posts and ensuing conversations in social media, annotated both for stance and veracity\" (Gorrell et al., 2019)."
